  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Travel of Slovak experts from the Office of Social Affairs and Family to Georgia</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Vyslanie expertov z &#xDA;radu pr&#xE1;ce, soci&#xE1;lnych vec&#xED; a rodiny SR do Gruz&#xED;nska</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">&lt;p&gt;Cie&#x13E;om vyslania expertov bolo:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Vytvori&#x165; anal&#xFD;zu syst&#xE9;mu soci&#xE1;lnych benefitov a defin&#xED;cie jednotliv&#xFD;ch kateg&#xF3;ri&#xED; recipientov. Zavedenie syst&#xE9;mu hodnotenia potrieb a jasn&#xE9; ur&#x10D;enie podmienok poskytovania &#x161;t&#xE1;tnych soci&#xE1;lnych pr&#xED;spevkov, finan&#x10D;n&#xE1; a nefinan&#x10D;n&#xE1; pomoc (slu&#x17E;by). Zv&#xFD;&#x161;enie motiv&#xE1;cie pr&#xED;jemcov a zv&#xFD;&#x161;enie povedomia o slu&#x17E;b&#xE1;ch poskytovan&#xFD;ch Ministerstvom pr&#xE1;ce, zdravia a soci&#xE1;lnych vec&#xED; a &#xA0;Agent&#xFA;rou soci&#xE1;lnych slu&#x17E;ieb Gruz&#xED;nska.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;The mission of the experts was to:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Create an analysis of the social benefits system and the definitions of each recipient category. Establishment of needs assessment system and clear definition of conditions for the provision of state social contributions, financial and non-financial assistance (services). Increase recipient motivation and raise awareness of services provided by the Ministry of Labor, Health and Social Affairs and the Georgian Social Services Agency.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
